# ─── WHAT WE DO COMMIT ────────────────────────────────────
# ✅ src/                     — all source code
# ✅ notebooks/               — structured notebook series
# ✅ kaggle/                  — Kaggle notebooks
# ✅ team/                    — team member work (scripts only)
# ✅ deployment/              — Gradio + FastAPI
# ✅ config/config.yaml       — configuration
# ✅ docs/                    — documentation + PDFs
# ✅ scripts/                 — runnable scripts
# ✅ results/results_all.json — verified results ledger
# ✅ results/master_results.csv
# ✅ results/plots/           — PNG plots
# ✅ data/demo/               — small demo datasets
# ✅ requirements.txt, setup.py, environment.yml
# ✅ README.md, MASTER_PLAN.md, LICENSE
# ✅ .gitignore
